            <p class="article-lead">AI-powered PDF tools have become incredibly capable — summarizing contracts, extracting invoice data, answering questions about documents. But before uploading a client contract, a medical record, or a financial statement to any online AI tool, you need to understand exactly what happens to your data. This guide gives you the questions to ask and the red flags to avoid.</p>
